# 1. 🧩 Introduction

Block Tactics is a text-based Sokoban-style puzzle game implemented in C++.  
Players push boxes onto target positions within a 10×10 grid.

This project fulfills all required coding elements:

- Random events  
- Data structures  
- Dynamic memory management  
- File input/output  
- Multi-file structure  
- Multiple difficulty levels  

---

# 2. 🎮 Game Overview

The player must strategically push all boxes onto target positions.

The game emphasizes:

- Logical thinking  
- Planning ahead  
- Avoiding deadlocks  

